data.description:
Step inside this magnificent residence situated in the highly coveted Chateau neighborhood, where you can make yourself at home immediately! This energy-efficient home comes complete with fully paid-for solar power, ensuring substantial cost savings. The FIVE generously sized bedrooms are all conveniently located upstairs, each boasting ample closet space.

Your backyard serves as a tranquil oasis, featuring a patio that's perfect for outdoor relaxation and entertainment. In addition, the Chateau community offers an array of fantastic amenities, including a clubhouse, an outdoor pool, playgrounds, and tennis courts.

This fantastic location in Charlotte places you in close proximity to restaurants, shops, Carowinds, schools, and parks. Plus, easy access to I-77 makes commuting a breeze
